               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Mäṣḥafä gǝnzät “Book of the Funeral Ritual” (fols. 3ra- 120rb)&#xD;
- Introduction (fols.3ra-8vb)&#xD;
- Discourse of St. Athanasius on death (fols. 9ra-16rb)&#xD;
- Mäṣḥaf zä-wäḍʾat ʾǝm-ʾIyärusalem “Book that Came from Jerusalem” (fols. 16rb-22va)&#xD;
- Antiphons (kǝśtät, ʾaryam, sälam) (fols. 26vb-28va, 43rb-44rb, 48rb-48vb, 50rb-51va, 51va-52rb, 55rb, 57rb-58vb, 60rb, 61vb-62rb, 64vb-65ra, 68va-vb)&#xD;
- Homily by St. Jacob of Sarug for the funeral of priests and deacons (fols. 69va-72vb)&#xD;
- Homily by ʾabba Sälama, Metropolitan of Ethiopia (fols. 86ra-91va)&#xD;
- Lǝfafä ṣǝdq “Bandlet of Righteousness” (fols. 91va-94vb)&#xD;
- Mängädä sämay “Journey to Heaven” (fols. 94vb-95vb)&#xD;
&#xD;
Additio 1; colophon.</summary>
